chant: chant - Say a random explosive chant~
userlist: userlist - List all users on the current server
botlist: botlist - List all bots on the current server
help: help - Show all commands & command descriptions
xkcd: xkcd <int/str> - fetch the comic by id,random, or latest.
kick: kick <mention(s)> - Kick the mentioned user(s) from the guild.
vote: vote <str,CSV> - Start a vote with the specified questions.
